CM_ BO_ 285 "Comm_201: chassis diagnostic request.";
CM_ BO_ 286 "Comm_201: chassis diagnostic response.";
CM_ BO_ 288 "Comm_201: brake wear extension.";
CM_ BO_ 289 "Comm_201: road friction extension.";

